OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FSome late
OL,6,Fevening brightness as clear periods
OL,7,Fdevelop and winds begin to slowly
OL,8,Fease. Any residual showers will
OL,9,Fgradually fade to leave a dry and
OL,10,Fchilly night.
OL,11,
OL,12,CSaturday:FDry, increasingly cloudy
OL,13,Fmorning. Patchy afternoon rain, mainly
OL,14,Facross western hills. Winds
OL,15,Fstrengthening, with gales perhaps
OL,16,Fsevere gales developing into the
OL,17,Fevening, as a heavy rain band moves
OL,18,Feast.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
