OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FStrong
OL,6,Fwinds and coastal gales easing Sunday
OL,7,Fmorning, followed by scattered
OL,8,Fblustery showers, wintry over higher
OL,9,Fground. Sunshine and lighter winds
OL,10,FMonday; breezier Tuesday but staying
OL,11,Fdry and sunny. Warmer.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
